Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.78,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)}本字幕由喵萌奶茶屋製作 僅供交流試看之用 請勿用於商業用途{\fscy20}\N\N{\r}翻譯：番茄雞　時軸：Ronny　後期：MIR　繁化：錯黨　特效：A5
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.83,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,杏奈ちゃん　いいところに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これ　バレンタインのチョコです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:16.87,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.37,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:19.60,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,かわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:21.38,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,かわわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,くるり
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.52,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう１往復しようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.11,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう５往復目だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.15,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ソワソワソワ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,こんなに集まったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.56,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それはよかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:37.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ねえねえ　ちぃは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.17,Dial-JP,,0,800,0,,一応　かあさんに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.47,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いつもと変わらない日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.51,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,２月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:42.97,Dial-JP,,0,800,0,,よかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.51,Dial-JP,,0,800,0,,いやいや　家族だから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:46.40,Dial-JP,,0,800,0,,うんうん　よかったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:49.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,義理チョコ　撲滅運動しようぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:54.31,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,勘違いする悲しき男子をこれ以上増やしたくないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:56.70,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:58.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,早い者勝ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.38,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,撲滅運動は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ハトみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:09.05,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,早くどけてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.87,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,取った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:10.53,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:11.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,じゃああげる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:12.13,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いらん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そう言うと思って　イッチの机で広げたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:21.56,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日は男子なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:23.92,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんという卑しさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,おい　見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:29.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ここのナッツハート形じゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:31.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,隠れ本命って事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.37,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,浮かれすぎだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:33.99,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あげるんじゃなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:34.71,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.96,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコをもらうだけで勘違いするだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:38.83,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ピュアなんだよ　男は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.12,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川もそうだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.83,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ピュア・シンデレラ・ボーイだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:42.65,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,黙れ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.97,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日は将棋をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ルール知らないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.39,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,将棋は将棋でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チロルチョコ将棋だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:24.53,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,バーン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや　もっとわからん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:36.05,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,その手があったか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.15,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どの手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.55,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川も言って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.21,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,その手が…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.25,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いつだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.88,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いくら考えてもわかる気がしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.05,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうなったら勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,参りました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:02.00,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,勝ったほうが　駒を総取りってルール
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.28,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.61,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.61,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコだな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.04,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もらったチョコ見せろ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.15,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,おめえのチョコにはハートないな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.23,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,義理だ　よし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.34,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ああはなるまい　ああは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:42.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱギリって書いてあるやつにすりゃよかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:46.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,結局さ　チョコあげるだけで満足してちゃダメだにゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,気持ち伝わんなきゃ意味ない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:05:01.39,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや　山田がお菓子を人に与える事自体が珍しい事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これもいつもの山田の奇行の一つということで正解なのだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.01,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,走りにくい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.44,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.43,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,人のチョコをうらやむとは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.16,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:27.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日は奇行が多いな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:35.44,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,しかし　何も学校で渡さなくてもいいのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　原さんたちなんて一緒に帰ったり　デ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.70,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,デートする仲だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いつでも渡せるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.69,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,一日は長い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.75,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,学校は学びの場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これはやっかみではない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:52.61,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.67,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.72,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,横乗り怖っ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.97,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もっとゆっくり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,一日は長いから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:14.11,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,またしちゃったね　２人乗り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,前した時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,交番の前通るの死ぬかと思ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.00,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,気づかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.28,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,降りるように言おうかと思ったけど　あの時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.99,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,変化を恐れるタイプだね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.81,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,って言われて　なんかムキになって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.20,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,私そんな事言った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.37,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,確かにそのとおりだと思った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.23,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,山田は変化を楽しむタイプだから　わからんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:40.89,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:45.88,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今なら　わかるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今が幸せだからかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.15,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,い…　いや　まだ足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.55,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だっておなかすいた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.16,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱ高いな　こういうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.15,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,チョコまん買ったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,１年の女子にいっぱいチョコもらったんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.05,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいの　チョコは無限に入るの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.84,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,一目で義理とわかるチョコ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.65,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,取らん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川はチョコ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.52,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや　んっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.52,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川はさ　どんなチョコなら本命だって思うの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.89,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと言われないとわかんないかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.92,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.47,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ハート形なら勘違いする奴いるかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,足立が言ってたんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:19.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あげる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.65,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ついてる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.28,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,バイバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ほんの少し…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,心のどっかで期待してた
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.27,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと言われないとわかんないかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,い…　いたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.67,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　頑張れ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.34,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,これ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,山田　教室で言ってたろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日は男子だって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.74,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日は男子なの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.25,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.00,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いち…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.35,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,よし　よしよし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そういうことだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,正解だよな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.40,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって山田だし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,絶対キモい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんだよ　メルティーキッスって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.66,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,とろけるキッス
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.06,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,見るの怖っ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.53,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,２月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.01,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,19時26分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:09.48,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんか　わん太郎のお散歩コース変えてみようかなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そういや　市川んち近いなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.04,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっと語ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.97,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.48,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,持ってみる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.84,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.51,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと握って
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:32.89,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,こんな感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.59,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,よーし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.70,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,欲しいココアと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.39,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,一番欲しくないブラックコーヒーを
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.29,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,同時に押してスリルを味わうやーつ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.95,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それギャンブルなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.28,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうしてだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.54,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,しょうがないからあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ども
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.09,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でさ　ちぃがアリをそのままにして
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありのままとか言ってたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.54,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あとね…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,えっとね…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.24,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日　山田変だな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.79,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.11,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いつも変だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:29.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.13,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうかって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.03,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ってか自分で言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.87,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いつもちぃに言われるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ちぃはいないので　自分で言った
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.92,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,寒くない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.99,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.01,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今日チョコありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:47.19,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今年は暖かいね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.26,Dial-JP,,0,600,0,,もう　雪降らないのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.13,Dial-JP,,600,0,0,,なんの時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,い…　いち…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.38,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,市川は今日　チョコもらった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,家族以外に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:03.93,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.39,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ってルール
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.22,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,今だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あげる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.25,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:19.90,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やま…　山田は　チョコあげた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.48,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,この質問セーフか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:25.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:29.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,だって義理チョコ　あげない事にしたし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,勝ったほうが駒を総取り
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.17,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あげる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:41.67,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,まあ　義理チョコなんて撲滅したほうがいいという
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.43,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,足立の意見には同意だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,勘違いする不幸な男が生まれるだけなので
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.38,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,苦い？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.98,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,甘いものが苦手と言ったのはウソなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.46,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.29,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,甘く　作りすぎちゃったから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.56,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ス？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.18,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もぎっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.60,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:30.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:38.60,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,勘違いしても　いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:49.18,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,山田は…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.30,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,うまくできなくて　全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,うまいうまい　普通に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.29,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや　普通とかじゃなくて　すごく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.65,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.56,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう一回して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.12,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,山田は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.17,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうした　難しい顔して
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.57,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ホワイトデーのお返し　なんにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,まだ１カ月前なんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいや
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もう１カ月しかないとも言える
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:41.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そう　僕は山田にチョコをもらった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.59,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もらったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.52,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ひと月後のホワイトデー
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.78,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,僕はいいお返しができるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.28,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,この１カ月　どう生きるかが重要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.04,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,関根がばらまいてたやつだけだろ　もらったの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.29,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ナッツがハート形だったし
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　女子って　察してちゃんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.04,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はっきり言ってやんなよ　萌ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.43,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,義理　本命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ご想像にお任せしまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,悪女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.63,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やはり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,萌　イヤーポッドが欲しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:17.08,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱさ　素敵　センスある　抱いて　２番目でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:19.82,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,って言われるプレゼントしたいよな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,はべらせ願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.93,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱここは　エッチな下着か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.64,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,何がやっぱなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.72,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,手作りチョコをもらったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.70,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,手作り下着か
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.45,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,社会的に死ぬだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:35.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,僕はスイーツ食べ放題でもごちそうしようかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それいいな　食べ放題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.13,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,誘うのが大変だが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.40,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,おめえ　チョコもらったんか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.34,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,まあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ウソをついても仕方ない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.10,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,どうせブスだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.48,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,というか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,好きでもない相手のお返しなんて適当でいいのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.12,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,俺は俺の事を好きな奴が好きなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.78,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,フラグは　多ければ多いほうがいいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.33,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,一本も立ってないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:24.87,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,考えてみりゃ俺　関根の事　なんにも知らないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.71,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,知らないから怖いし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,適当にはできないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.75,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,真面目だな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.07,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ってかどこに連れてかれてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:36.72,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.85,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,南条パイセン　委員会で一緒でさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.59,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,なんか消えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.99,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,パイセンめっちゃモテっからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.62,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,アドバイスもらおうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,生きてたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.32,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,全然モテないよ　俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.98,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,またまた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.14,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ただこう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:55.16,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いけそうな雰囲気を察知できるというか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.88,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そういう空気　を読めるかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.19,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,読めてないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.18,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,こいつも　バレンタインにチョコもらったみたいなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.04,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,お返し　何がいいんすかね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.00,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,もらったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:17.69,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,でも俺は相手の好みとかよく知らないんで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.44,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱ知ってから選んだほうがいいんすかね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.70,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いいや　そんなの意味ないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.52,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,男と女は　そもそも一生わかり合えないものだからね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.44,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:29.73,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.48,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,全く違う生き物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.30,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,環境も趣味も考え方も違ってて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:41.06,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,それでも知っていくうちに似ている部份がどっかにあったりして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:41.99,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,共感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.41,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,というより　理解できるようになるものでは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.62,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,何がいいんすかね　プレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.80,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,下着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.38,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,とかは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.94,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱありっすよね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,絶対喜んでもらえると思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.42,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,ねっ　市原くん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.04,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,下手くそな罠だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.30,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.11,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱ　パイセンの話はタメになるな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,そうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:17.19,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,俺にとっては足立のほうが　学びや気づきになること言ってるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.68,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,俺は好きにならないかんな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.47,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,部活行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.26,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,俺　帰ります
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.66,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,やめ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.49,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,俺は　山田を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.58,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,待て待て
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.06,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,す…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.00,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,す…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.77,Dial-JP,,0,0,0,,さよなら
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue Chinese
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,杏奈 來得正好
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這個送妳 情人節巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.09,0:00:16.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還有我的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.96,0:00:19.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.60,0:00:21.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,愛死了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.64,0:00:25.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,折返
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再走一個來回吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,已經5個來回了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,激動激動
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,看 我收了這麼多
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那妳可真厲害
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.56,0:00:37.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.81,0:00:40.17,Dial-CH,,0,800,0,,媽媽給了一個
Dialogue: 1,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,平平無奇的一天
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,2月14日
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.65,0:00:42.97,Dial-CH,,0,800,0,,挺好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.51,Dial-CH,,0,800,0,,家人不算數
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.51,0:00:46.40,Dial-CH,,0,800,0,,嗯嗯 那也挺好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.40,0:00:49.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,朋友巧克力取締運動 開始
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.90,0:00:54.31,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒人想看到產生誤會的男生再增加了對吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.69,0:00:56.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,來拿吧
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.70,0:00:58.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,先到先得
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,取締運動呢
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,像一群鴿子
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.63,0:01:09.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,快拿走
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你拿了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.87,0:01:10.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.53,0:01:11.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那送你了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.35,0:01:12.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就知道你會這樣說 所以我才放你桌上的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.23,0:01:21.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,人家今天是男生
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老子今天是
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.41,0:01:23.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,何等不要臉
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.19,0:01:27.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,喂 來看啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.09,0:01:29.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這塊堅果是心形的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.07,0:01:31.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,她暗戀我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,太能妄想了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.37,0:01:33.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,早知道不給他了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.99,0:01:34.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.96,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是個男生收到巧克力都會誤會的啊
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.96,0:01:38.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我們男生就是這麼純情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你不也是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.83,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,純情灰姑娘男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.83,0:01:42.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今天來下將棋吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我不懂規則啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.80,0:03:22.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,說是將棋
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,其實是方塊巧克力將棋
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.79,0:03:24.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,砰
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,更不懂了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.01,0:03:36.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,原來還有這一手啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.05,0:03:37.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哪一手
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你也說一句
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.21,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還有這一…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是現在
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那什麼時候說啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼想都想不通
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼才算贏…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.05,0:03:53.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.79,0:04:02.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,獲勝方得到所有棋子 就是規則
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,現在說
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,巧克力…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,收到了巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是收到了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,讓我看看你收到的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好像是沒看到心形
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好 你這是朋友巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不要像他那樣 絕不能
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.64,0:04:42.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,後悔了 應該寫上「朋友」兩個字的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.45,0:04:46.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還是不能只滿足於送了巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不明確表明送的意圖就沒意義了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,巧克力…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.37,0:05:01.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不對 山田送別人零食這事本身就不尋常
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.39,0:05:04.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,將其解釋為山田的又一個怪異行為或許更為妥當
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳扯著我很難跑
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這個送你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好羨慕
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.68,0:05:21.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,覬覦別人的巧克力不太好吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.39,0:05:27.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今天的怪異行為還真多
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.73,0:05:35.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,其實也不必非得在學校裡送吧
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,他們的關係不是好到能一起走回家 約…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,約會什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,什麼時候都能給啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一天時間很長
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,學校是用來學習的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我這不是酸啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.83,0:05:52.61,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,載我
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.95,0:06:01.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,橫著坐有點嚇人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你再騎慢點
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一天時間很長嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.11,0:06:14.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀 又載上了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,上次
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,經過派出所時我真以為要死了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我都沒發現
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我當時也想過要妳下去的 但
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,說明你是害怕變化的那類人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.81,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳說完這句話 我莫名有點賭氣了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.20,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我說過嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.37,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,當時覺得妳說得對
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.23,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳是喜愛變化的那類人 估計妳是不懂的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.72,0:06:40.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.91,0:06:45.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,現在可能懂了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可能因為現在太幸福了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不… 不行 還不夠
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.55,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因為肚子餓了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這種巧克力確實貴啊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.15,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,買的是巧克力餡的包子嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是收了很多初一學妹的巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.05,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你別管 巧克力多少都吃得下
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一眼就能看出全是朋友巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不給你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我又不要
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川今天 巧…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不 就是…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.63,0:07:47.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎樣你才會覺得收到的是真愛巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不太懂
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可能對方不明說我就不會明白吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,很難說
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有人可能看到心形就會誤會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,足立是這樣說的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.95,0:08:19.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,送你了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嘴邊沾了點
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,內心深處…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,其實稍稍有一點期待的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.27,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可能對方不明說我就不會明白吧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳… 妳還沒走啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒事 大膽一點
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳在教室裡不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳今天是男生
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.74,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,人家今天是男生
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,老子今天是
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.35,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好 很好很好
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是這個意思吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,應該是對的吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,畢竟她是山田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,絕對很噁心
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼偏偏選了個Meltykiss啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,深情一吻是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.49,0:10:43.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不敢看
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.53,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,2月14日
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,19點26分
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.02,0:11:09.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今天不知道為什麼想給汪太郎換條散步路線
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然後順路到了你家附近
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,找個地方聊一會吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.04,0:11:16.97,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,牽一下試試
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.48,0:11:22.84,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不會出問題吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.51,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,要握緊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.78,0:11:32.89,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對 就這樣
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,賭一把吧
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,把我想喝的熱可可
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,和我最不愛的黑咖啡
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,的按鈕同時按下 驚險刺激
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.95,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這算賭博嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.90,0:12:00.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 給你喝吧
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.53,0:12:06.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我謝謝妳
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.09,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然後千千就放著螞蟻不管
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.09,0:12:16.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,還說什麼「保持原樣」
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.54,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,然後呢…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我想想哦…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.24,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳今天好怪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.60,0:12:24.79,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我覺得
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我一直都很怪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.11,0:12:29.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,別同意啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.03,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼自己說自己怪啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,總是千千說我的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,現在她不在 我就自己說啦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.37,0:12:40.92,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你冷不冷啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.92,0:12:41.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不冷
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.01,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝你送的巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.27,0:12:47.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,今年冬天真暖和
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.26,Dial-CH,,0,600,0,,是不是不會下雪了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.13,Dial-CH,,600,0,0,,好混亂的對話
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市… 市…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,市川 你今天收到巧克力了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,除了家人給的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.89,0:13:03.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.39,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,就是規則
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.22,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,現在說
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,送你了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.25,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.90,0:13:19.90,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山… 山田呢 送了誰嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這個提問應該沒問題吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.71,0:13:25.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,沒啊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.15,0:13:29.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因為已經想好了不送朋友巧克力了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,獲勝方得到所有棋子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,送你了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.47,0:13:41.67,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,確實 我覺得朋友巧克力這東西是該取締
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我同意足立的想法
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,因為這只會讓更多男生會錯意然後傷心
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,苦嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我騙了妳 其實我不討厭甜的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.46,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那正好
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我做得太甜了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.47,0:14:15.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,Su？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,掰開
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.43,0:14:28.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.94,0:14:30.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.79,0:14:38.60,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你可以會錯意
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.06,0:14:49.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田她…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒做好
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好吃好吃 挺好吃的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不是 是非常好吃
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.65,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.56,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再抱一次
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山田她…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.17,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 表情這麼嚴肅
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.57,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,白色情人節的回禮買什麼好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這不還有一個月呢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,錯
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這意味著只剩一個月了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.02,0:16:41.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對 我收到了山田的巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真收到了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.41,0:16:46.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,一個月後就是白色情人節
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我能給出一個好的回禮嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.78,0:16:52.28,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這一個月怎麼活 這很關鍵
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你收到的不就是關根發的嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.29,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但我收到的那上面有愛心
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你想啊 女生都很靦腆的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,妳就明明白白告訴他吧 小萌
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.43,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,朋友 真愛
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,任君想像
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,壞女人
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.63,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,好想要藍牙耳機呀
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.45,0:17:17.08,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,能讓她說出「你好有品味 想給你生孩子 不介意當小妾」
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.08,0:17:19.82,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,的這種禮物是最好的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,純純的白日做夢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.93,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就是情趣內衣了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.64,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,怎麼得出的結論
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我收到的是手作巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那就送手作內衣嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.45,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,那你以後別想在社會上混了
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.45,0:17:35.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我要不就請她吃甜點自助大餐吧
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.10,0:17:37.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這個好啊 自助餐
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.13,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,雖然發出邀約是有點難
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.67,0:17:46.40,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你收到巧克力了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,算
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.34,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,說謊也什麽用
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.10,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,反正肯定是醜女送的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.48,0:18:13.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你也不喜歡她 回禮隨意點不就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.12,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我喜歡喜歡我的人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.78,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,替補女友肯定是越多越好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.33,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你一個也沒有
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.33,0:18:24.87,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這樣一想 我發現我根本不了解關根啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.71,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不了解所以怕送得不對
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,肯定不能太隨意的
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.75,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這麼認真啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.07,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,話說你要帶我去哪裡
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.82,0:18:36.72,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這是南條學長 我們都是年級委員
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.44,0:18:41.59,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,人影怎麼變淡了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,學長可討女生喜歡了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.99,0:18:45.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,讓他給點建議吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這人還活著啊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.32,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我可不討女生喜歡
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.98,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,又謙虛了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.14,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.14,0:18:55.16,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,如果誰對我有意思
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.88,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,或者好感 我能感覺得到吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.88,0:18:59.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你不能
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.18,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,這小子也收到了女生給的情人節巧克力
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,您覺得回禮送什麼好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.64,0:19:13.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你收到了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.42,0:19:17.69,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,但我不太清楚對方喜歡什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是不是先去了解一下再買比較好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.70,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,不啊 這沒意義的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.70,0:19:26.52,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,男人和女人永遠都無法相互理解
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.44,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,有道理
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.44,0:19:29.73,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,真是如此嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.48,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,雖然兩種截然不同的生物
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.38,0:19:37.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,生活環境 興趣 思維方式也不同
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.30,0:19:41.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,可在熟識的過程中 發現雙方也有些相似
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.06,0:19:41.99,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,進而產生共鳴
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.42,0:19:46.41,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,換句話說 這正是在逐漸理解對方吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.62,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,所以禮物到底選什麼好呢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.80,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,內衣
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.38,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.94,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,您也覺得這個好 是吧
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,對方肯定會喜歡的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.42,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你說是吧 市原
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.04,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,顯而易見的陷阱
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.44,0:20:11.11,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,聽學長一席話 勝讀十年書啊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.07,0:20:17.19,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得你說的話更讓我如夢初醒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.31,0:20:20.68,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我不會喜歡上你的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.47,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,該去社團了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.26,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我回家了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.66,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,別…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.49,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我 喜歡…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.58,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你先打住
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.06,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.00,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,山…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.77,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,再見
